Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻摇动的死亡之影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲惨的命运 迷失的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨与被憎恨之间产生的裂缝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有如双面镜般的双生茧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从时间混杂的黑暗中走来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的怨恨 由我来消除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.06,0:01:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的景色我已经看腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.71,0:02:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.09,0:02:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不腻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.51,0:02:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪玖理我已经看够了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过于习惯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.58,0:02:21.54,题名,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说过那事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个在报纸上也登过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是个那么小的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开窗户
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈…妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲很严厉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在国外生活了十年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了这么久又回到日本住下了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西让你痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在怀疑我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我说了也没人相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害了妈妈 把爸爸伤成这样的犯人消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被流放到地狱去了…什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系的 不要担心 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子 看啊 恶魔之子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他杀了自己的母亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连父亲也要杀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有被杀死到现在为止还一直住院呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始是杀了附近的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来玩腻了就杀了双亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不敢相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那样平时看起来老实的孩子才是最可怕的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么警察不把他抓起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么证据不足的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然好像已经进行证据调查了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:04:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那之后已经三个月了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再发生事件的话怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在步行街里骑摩托车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是住在Lovely Hills的孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不是也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道我的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你是演员什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我吃一口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌甜瓜面包的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫芹 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来这里要建一个车站的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓真你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听爸爸说过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么没有建的理由是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像因为泡沫破裂了 便中止了计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs18}（这里的泡沫指泡沫经济）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底就是没钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得就是活该
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁了我家的新房去建什么车站
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里曾经是我的新家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我父母好像不太喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿了钱就笑眯眯的交出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里曾经是湖岔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年一到春天就会有很多青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然夜里会很吵闹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我很喜欢那个声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都是青蛙的叫声？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样很吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我经常夜里偷溜出来看它们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还被骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为青蛙一叫 就不会去留意父母吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 要打起精神生活哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家没有人 不用太客气的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 就让你搭讪一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我给你做晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是会很难吃的哦 你要做好心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说“哎”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说“拜托你了”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要坐这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 难道你有什么意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样很不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说“这样”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很喜欢坐它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓真也要做吗 很痛快的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:08:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:08:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这样做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是做了坏事 一定会有报应的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近知了在叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都习惯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人坐没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可头盔只有一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 今天回来得真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识莲江先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个是…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芹你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么骗你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不难吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么不是很好吗 不要抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是抱怨 是在夸你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就直接夸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说拓真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起离开这个城市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芹要去什么地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里已经不是我所认识的城市了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为爸爸还在住院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快…就走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要随便就进来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女也来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女？那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是动画片什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你落伍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对情报什么的很不灵通的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老土 老土
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了 闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老土 老土
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪玖理又出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她回收了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:12:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的纪玖理又来打扰府上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是纪玖理的妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪玖理 是你妈妈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪玖理 衣服衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪玖理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来做什么 大婶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这孩子这样做是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便跑到别人家去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓真知道我不是人类哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是人类是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 那个 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪玖理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个大婶可是妖怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 会变成骨头的骨女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.71,0:13:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪玖理 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:13:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 真是…打扰您了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有谁访问网页了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了把怨恨的对象流放到地狱去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓真
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个一定是迷信啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个哦 是都市传说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 因为我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我面前 人就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的啊 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 钱准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要找理由 约好是昨天哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚内准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是突然要那么大笔钱是很难的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难也要准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上我就去取
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的吧 莲江先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把钱放在信箱里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你听到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在勒索莲江先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真聪明啊 连这个都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芹…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要说“不要做坏事”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要离开这个城市就需要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要勒索莲江先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勒索谁都一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是凑巧知道莲江的事情罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是开发Lovely Hills的建筑公司的董事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一听说是毁了我新家的那个公司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.88,0:16:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想着“好 就这个家伙了”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对拓真你不太好说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想听
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我调查了莲江的生活规律
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假装偶然去接近他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后和他约会了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就正中我下怀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把和未成年的我的关系向公司揭穿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对他说“不想被揭穿的话就给我钱”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.10,0:17:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是什么都没做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这就像是复仇一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起好色之心就是那人不对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓真长大后就会明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后莲江那家伙约好要付钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却在那拖延时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有办法 就直接跑他家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:17:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实什么都没有做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但丈夫一直说着没有的事没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子会相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就有了刚才的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开这里想去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里的乡下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是有很多青蛙的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都会从头开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把迄今为止的事情全部忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 去睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要要什么钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住我家吧 一直在这里也可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓真 谢谢你 我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我安定下来就和你联络
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你父亲好起来以后要来玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在很痛苦 但是要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有些家伙说些奇怪的话 也别管它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为拓真就是拓真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓真可不是孤单一人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要把我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是拓真哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认收到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾已闻汝之恨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.73,0:21:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去地狱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被人怨恨所以被流放了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.14,0:22:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是那个城市的错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.43,0:22:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不建成那个城市的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 害人者亦害己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 让我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 求你了 让我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.36,0:22:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股怨恨 将流向地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.66,0:22:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 让我回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.24,0:23:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的怨恨 我来消除
